org.matsim.contrib.smartcity.agent

Class AbstractDriverLogic

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.smartcity.agent.AbstractDriverLogic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SmartDriverLogic
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StaticDriverLogic

    public abstract class AbstractDriverLogic
extends java.lang.Object
implements SmartDriverLogic
    Abstract class that implements a standard behavior of an agent logic. This simplify the implementations of SmartDriverLogic interface. The only abstract method is chooseNextLinkId; implement in this method the smart behavior of agent. Furthermore is possible overriding all methods of SmartDriverLogic interface.
    Author:
    Filippo Muzzini
